graduated from the University of
Pittsburgh in 1961 with a BBA, and
attended the Graduate Business Program
at the University of Mjnnesota—Deluth,
from 1976-1979. He is on the Board of
Directors of the Greater Pittsburgh
Council, Boy Scouts of America, and is
a member of the Pennsylvania Institute
of Certiﬁed Public Accountants.

